    "name": "Taverna",
    "steam_appid": 3219160,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Taverna 是一款第一人称冒险游戏，背景设定在一个在线酒馆的世界中。创建并定制属于你的酒馆，或与最多16名玩家（每个大厅）一起探索其他酒馆。赚取金币，完成任务，解锁物品，享受角色扮演的乐趣。</i></strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>定制你的酒馆</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/8ffd425ead42794151b3815de4012d94.poster.avif?t=1748280912\" width=680 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/8ffd425ead42794151b3815de4012d94.webm?t=1748280912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/8ffd425ead42794151b3815de4012d94.mp4?t=1748280912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>粉刷</strong>墙壁，<strong>添加家具</strong>，<strong>灯光</strong>和<strong>装饰</strong>，营造独特氛围。酒馆中的每一个细节都可以由你定制，打造一个欢迎朋友和冒险者的温馨场所。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>语音聊天！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/9cc3c9e37d36ed962912aa69beb3a64d.poster.avif?t=1748280912\" width=680 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/9cc3c9e37d36ed962912aa69beb3a64d.webm?t=1748280912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/9cc3c9e37d36ed962912aa69beb3a64d.mp4?t=1748280912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>与其他玩家进行语音交流</strong>，以有趣且互动的方式沟通。组织脱口秀之夜，或与朋友共度美好时光。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>自由创造</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/ca512bd08b533437f8724f4a4e6f0e1a.poster.avif?t=1748280912\" width=680 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/ca512bd08b533437f8724f4a4e6f0e1a.webm?t=1748280912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/ca512bd08b533437f8724f4a4e6f0e1a.mp4?t=1748280912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多种方式表达自我</strong>：包括<strong>绘画、装饰、演奏乐器</strong>和<strong>定制环境</strong>。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>沉浸于奇幻世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/f901461e9cfec199e0e975278d954aa0.poster.avif?t=1748280912\" width=680 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/f901461e9cfec199e0e975278d954aa0.webm?t=1748280912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/f901461e9cfec199e0e975278d954aa0.mp4?t=1748280912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索一个舒适的奇幻酒馆</strong>，仿佛直接来自你最喜爱的故事或游戏。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>其他特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从超过<strong>15种角色</strong>中选择。无论你选择成为<strong>厨师</strong>、<strong>吟游诗人</strong>还是<strong>旅行者</strong>，这一选择将通过在头顶显示特殊标签，塑造你在 Taverna 中的角色扮演体验。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >赚取金币，用于<strong>解锁独特物品</strong>，推动你的酒馆发展。<strong>椅子</strong>、<strong>锅具</strong>、<strong>书籍</strong>、<strong>餐具</strong>、<strong>材料</strong>、<strong>颜料</strong>等多种物品。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >参与各种游戏和社交活动，让每次游戏都独一无二。从经典酒馆游戏到举办主题活动，Taverna 是角色扮演聚会的理想场所。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验基于<strong>物理</strong>的新互动层面。<strong>投掷</strong>、<strong>翻转</strong>、<strong>进食</strong>、<strong>饮用</strong>、<strong>摆姿势</strong>、<strong>拾取</strong>等多种操作……每个物品都可以以多种方式使用，常常带来意想不到的效果。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成任务，解锁新角色。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
